                        <interp inst="t18471213-name-148" type="given" value="CALEB EDWARD"></interp>CALEB EDWARD POWELL.</persName>
                  </hi> The half-crown and shilling are both counter<lb></lb>feit.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> The shilling was given to me; I did not know it was bad; I never had the half-crown.</p>
